splay:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\">\n        <svg width='20' height='20' fill='white' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z'\/><\/svg>\n      <\/div>\n      <h3 style=\"margin:0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#3C7D47;\">MISI KAMI<\/h3>\n    <\/div>\n    <ol style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#444444;margin:0;padding-left:20px;\">\n      <li>Menyediakan solusi engineering inovatif &amp; berkelanjutan di 4 bidang fokus SURIOTA.<\/li>\n      <li>Memanfaatkan teknologi terkini untuk meningkatkan efisiensi dan produktivitas klien.<\/li>\n      <li>Membangun hubungan saling menguntungkan melalui layanan cepat, akurat, dan berkualitas.<\/li>\n      <li>Memperkuat kompetensi tim dari skala nasional menuju internasional.<\/li>\n      <li>Menjadi mitra terpercaya dengan menjunjung tinggi Integritas dan Kredibilitas.<\/li>\n    <\/ol>\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-323e173 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"323e173\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc99e64\" data-id=\"cc99e64\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2c0322f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2c0322f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-512x512.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-898\" alt=\"about logo\" srcset=\"https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-512x512.jpg 512w, https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ef5419 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8ef5419\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:48px;align-items:center;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;\">\n  <div style=\"flex:0 0 auto;text-align:center;\">\n    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/suriota.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/about-logo-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Logo SURIOTA\" style=\"width:180px;height:180px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(32,91,105,0.14);\"\/>\n  <\/div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:260px;\">\n    <span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#EAF4EC;color:#3C7D47;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:14px;\">Tentang Kami<\/span>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#205B69;margin:0 0 14px;line-height:1.3;\">Siapa SURIOTA?<\/h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#444;margin:0 0 12px;\">SURIOTA adalah perusahaan <strong>engineering services<\/strong> berbasis di Batam, Kepulauan Riau \u2014 spesialis teknik elektrikal, otomasi industri, water treatment, dan energi terbarukan untuk industri dan infrastruktur Indonesia.<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#444;margin:0 0 12px;\">Dalam satu dekade beroperasi, kami menyelesaikan <strong>64+ proyek engineering<\/strong> \u2014 dari panel industri, IoT &amp; SCADA, WTP untuk PDAM Tirta Kepri, hingga PLTS hybrid off-grid. Setiap proyek dikerjakan dengan standar teknis internasional.<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#444;margin:0;\">Kami juga mengembangkan produk teknologi in-house: platform IIoT <strong style=\"color:#205B69;\">SURGE<\/strong> dan modem gateway <strong style=\"color:#205B69;\">SRT-MGATE-1210<\/strong>.<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7d665b8 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"7d665b8\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8772e75\" data-id=\"8772e75\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-85b06e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"85b06e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div